    "summary": "\u25cbBusiness Development \u25cbOperations&Continuous Improvement \u25cbLeading Change \u25cbStrategy to Action\n\nExpressive, enthusiastic, ambitious senior leader with unique mix of experience in commerce and manufacturing. Instrumental in creating customer development and NPD driven growth. Managing the growth in B2B and B2C and omnichannel envorinments with own brands, private labels and e-commerce sales. Ability to motivate and mobilise people on different levels and building performing teams. Holistic view on leading and managing the companies\u2019 processes, people, systems and communication with understanding of the big picture and small picture. All round senior manager in multicultural and multinational, PE- backed and family owned environments.\n\nExpertise\no Developing and executing strategic programs.\no Developing New Business.\no Facilitating growth and building an innovation environment.\no Skilled in initiating and perpetuating change.\no Knowledge of continuous improvement methodologies such as Lean and TPM.\no Turnaround Management and cost cutting.\no Building manufacturing, supply chain and distribution capability.\no Growing e-commerce B2B and B2C profitably\n\nTypical jobtitles which potentially brings up the best in Geert: Chief Executive Officer, CEO, Managing Director, MD, Chief Operations Officer, COO, Chief Commercial Officer, CCO.",
